{"tid":1079634,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"《閃亂神樂》製作人高木謙一郎離開 Marvelous","createTime":"2019-03-27T05:31:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-28T15:05:10.000Z","uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"bedec3c811559454dbae3bf396365a925fd62255","tid":1079634,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T05:31:59.000Z","msg":"根據日本 Fami 通網站報導，擔任《閃亂神樂》系列製作人、並有「爆乳製作人」暱稱的高木謙一郎已離開待了 13 年的老東家 Marvelous，不過仍會持續參與《閃亂神樂》系列開發。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/M/2KU/16/9cbc83c1843eb737e58bd481b10zsqw4.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FM%2F2KU%2F16%2F9cbc83c1843eb737e58bd481b10zsqw4.JPG&h=8c339685&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n　《閃亂神樂》系列首款作品是在 2011 年於 Nintendo 3DS 上發售的「爆乳動作戰鬥」遊戲《閃亂神樂 -少女們的真影-》，遊戲中隸屬於不同學院的女忍者們會演出「養眼搞笑」內容；隨後除了陸續推出多款本傳續作外，還衍生出《忍紓壓 閃亂神樂》、《PEACH BALL 閃亂神樂》等旁支作品並且動畫化，改編手機遊戲《忍者大師 閃亂神樂 NEW LINK》也已經在台開放預先註冊。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/M/2KU/99/d95a9b55cd7d7d4b9c596f811e13v135.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FM%2F2KU%2F99%2Fd95a9b55cd7d7d4b9c596f811e13v135.JPG&h=3745203f&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://gnn.gamer.com.tw/5/177235.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgnn.gamer.com.tw%2F5%2F177235.html&d=vajnz719fThxN7XVIZyF5YCLuBk19a2msHWYQfvuVO4%3D&h=702edfa1\" target=\"_blank\">https://gnn.gamer.com.tw/5/177235.html</a>"},{"pid":"a9901dbed7505ca17b3b2daaa2be98bc1a240ffc","tid":1079634,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T05:32:30.000Z","msg":"根據消息來源，明日在週刊 Fami 通 2019 年 4 月 11 日號（2019 年 3 月 28 日發售）以及 Fami 通網站上將會詳細刊載高木謙一郎的訪談內容，提及離開公司的理由以及《閃亂神樂》今後的動向，更將揭露未來在「新天地」的活動預定，以及 Marvelous 首度公開的全新跨媒體企劃。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/M/2KU/04/4d4489c52c419b085bf9cfe6a614d8s5.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FM%2F2KU%2F04%2F4d4489c52c419b085bf9cfe6a614d8s5.JPG&h=74427dda&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"6bce055b55cd6fe2964f7cf59b5ae77d74dd268f","tid":1079634,"uid":35814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T05:40:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2105036835491bb29abe24baed16196c5bb541c1","tid":1079634,"uid":21208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T11:11:27.000Z","msg":"我要新作呀師傅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e610bd6cc378a0c580e76a873227c0d0658cfde3","tid":1079634,"uid":42675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-28T15:05:10.000Z","msg":"佢隻正傳閃亂7開發到一半sony收緊哂啲審核，凶多吉少啦<br />\n不過依家走去CY都好<br />\nCY都開始發力搞主機GAME"}]}